## Limitations

This report is based on available literature and may not capture the full spectrum of research on the topic. The findings are subject to the limitations of the studies reviewed, including potential biases and the specific contexts in which the research was conducted. Additionally, the dynamic nature of economic systems means that the impact of inequality on growth can change over time and across different regions. Further research is needed to explore these dynamics in greater detail.

